{"tid":180581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局鬧笑話「dick sound」究竟係咩聲？","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T02:49:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":108,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e54bec2d081468ea97eca2de1fe87cd25069097","tid":180581,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490932226_ca5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490932226_ca5f.jpg&h=b7ccdf04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民Philip Heung fb截圖<br />\n<br />\n有網民發現教育局位於政府總部的辦公室，貼在門鈴上的指引鬧出笑話。據網民上載的圖片顯示，指引上寫道，「聽到『啲』一聲或紅燈轉綠燈後拉門進入」，惟『「啲」一聲』被譯成為「dick sound」，被網民反問應該是什麼聲音，嘲諷香港作為官方雙語的國際都市，政府機構竟然會犯這樣的低級錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n英語的擬聲詞通常以「beep」來形容門鈴聲，而根據劍橋英語詞典，「dick」用作名詞意指陰莖或笨蛋。<br />\n<br />\n【網民咁睇】<br />\nLun D.Chan：X叫呀，你碌X識唔識得叫呀<br />\nFrancis Lau：性教育局<br />\nMarco Yuen：啪啪啪聲？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56503615&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56503615%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170331&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=479bdd79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56503615%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170331&h=c2d101c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56503615&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170331</a>"},{"pid":"e19921b58af3afd8857dc6f1a5c80c5c9b3d983e","tid":180581,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /